config BR2_PACKAGE_TOUCH_TESTER
	bool "touch-tester"
	select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBGPIOD
	help
	  Touch latency measurement and testing utility for embedded systems.

	  This package provides tools for measuring touch input latency,
	  counting touch events, and generating test touch pulses using
	  GPIO-controlled capacitive auto-clickers.

	  Components:
	  - libtouch-test: Core library for GPIO control, touch event
	    reading, and latency measurement
	  - touch-tester: Command-line tool for automated testing
	  - qt-touch-tester: Qt5 GUI application with network daemon mode
	    (requires Qt5 to be enabled)

	  Typical use cases:
	  - Automotive head-unit touch display testing
	  - Touch controller latency characterization
	  - Touch event reliability testing

	  https://github.com/your-org/br-wrapper
